生凹陷。（海外网）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c9a5bdb389e68eae22a23c93850c8a1b_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "387 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469544314"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDY2NjIyODkwIKWP+4YGMBI4ngNAB3IJNDY5NTQ0MzE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1625310312.0854292", "card_id": "Q_468524945", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 92}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些曾经是平民食品现在却变得奢侈化的食物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "镜像问题：有哪些曾经是奢侈食品现在却变得平民化的食物？ - 知乎 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2359cb36bbaadbe6a6c442b6c16c3a60_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "363 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/468524945"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDY2Mzk2NDQ4IM+g5oYGMAI43AJACHIJNDY4NTI0OTQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1625310312.0861235", "card_id": "Q_469588431", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 Google Play 要求八月份起新应用须打包为 AAB 格式？对鸿蒙的发展有哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 1 日消息，据国外媒体报道，Google Play 将在今年 8 月进行颠覆性改变，谷歌应用商店的 App 格式将从「 APK 」改为「 Android App Bundles 」（ AAB）。 谷歌现在宣布从今年 8 月份开始，所有提交到 Google Play 商店的新应用必须采用 AAB 格式。 另外，谷歌在日前宣布，针对提供 WearOS 版本的应用，Google Play 开发者收入抽成由 30% 降至 15%。谷歌：Google Play 将启用 AAB 格式应用 取代安卓 APK"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-63e08d9d5424a0a5b51825c756323fd5_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "294 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469588431"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDY2NjMyNjkyIPzs+4YGMAQ4uwFACXIJNDY5NTg4NDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1625310312.0870507", "card_id": "Q_466361764", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 171}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些大道至简、直击本质的句子？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "类似于本人收集的如下句子： 1. 教育的本质是真正的教育，是一棵树撼动另一棵树，一片云推动另一片云，一个灵魂唤醒另一个灵魂——雅斯贝尔斯那 2. 正义的本质就是最好与最坏的折衷——所谓最好，就是干了坏事而不受罚；所谓最坏，就是受了罪而没法报复。 ——柏拉图《理想国》 3. 世界上最赚钱生意的本质是女人怕丑，老人怕死，小孩怕蠢，男人怕不行，穷人怕穷，中产怕返贫。 4. 金融的三个本质特点：一是为有钱人理财，为缺钱人融资；二是金融企业的核心要义在于信用、杠杆、风险三个环节调节；三是一切金融活动的目的是要为实体经济服务。 5. 怎样算是大格局？既能享受最好的，也能承受最坏的。 6. 洗脑的本质是用肢体的狂欢代替大脑的懒惰。 7. 赛博朋克的本质特点是高科技、低生活。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-28584ecb09c4b1c851e2a2a58e43abb0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "219 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466361764"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDY1OTE1NjAzILmqwYYGMAc4uQlACnIJNDY2MzYxNzY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1625310312.0880625", "card_id": "Q_469701438", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "感染幽门螺杆菌或诱发胃癌，家庭成员之间最容易传染，日常如何避免感染？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "幽门螺杆菌是目前所知能在人胃中生存的唯一微生物种类，容易引起慢性胃炎和消化性溃疡，与胃癌的发生息息相关，且家庭成员之间最容易相互传染。为了提高幽门螺杆菌早诊早治率，从 7 月 2 日起，江苏启动幽门螺杆菌家庭筛查项目。医生提醒，家庭中如果有人查出幽门螺杆菌感染，其他家庭成员也要及时做筛查，早发现、早治疗。感染幽门螺杆菌或诱发胃癌 医生：家人有人查出其他人也要赶快检查"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-ec7abeb299c7614a13ace4f0ee1016d0_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "212 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469701438"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDY2NjU3ODE1ILiZ/4YGMAM4iwNAC3IJNDY5NzAxNDM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1625310312.0888596", "card_id": "Q_466380653", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 491}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "给妈妈做了三个单元的教学 PPT，自己的署名被删了，应该生气吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "妈妈是大学老师，以前的 PPT 因为版本太老打不开了，只能重做。我看她工作量很大就主动提出来帮她做，做了大概三个单元的，花了两个星期左右 (每天都做)。除了文字内容没有改，版式和图表基本全部重做的，图片很多也特意去找的高清的，加了一些自己的想法 (提前征求了妈妈的意见)，用了点表情包，最后骄傲地署上了名。但去看她的教学视频后发现她把我开头结尾的署名全删了，讲课过程中也完全没有提到我帮她做了 PPT。 虽然确实是自愿做的，但还是很委屈。和她聊了之后她表示这些会分散她学生的注意力，没必要提及，且认为我不应该和她计较这些。 所以大吵了一架，现在不知道自己发这么大火是不是做错了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c3c25da1c2e41b2a50198bfb2e35020b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "193 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466380653"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDY1OTE5NzkxIKbZwYYGMGo47QlADHIJNDY2MzgwNjUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1625310312.0897171", "card_id": "Q_275348817", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 77}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "医院的电梯为什么会有专人操作？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一个看起来没什么技术含量的岗位为什么依然存在，主要作用是什么呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d4b40988e4d96f16ccfd45d19ae04dbe_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "174 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/275348817"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3a7y4Izj4oVAEAMaCDIzNDY0MzEzILy3mdcFMAM49QFADXIJMjc1MzQ4ODE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1625310312.0902202", "card_id": "EV_12217215", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "百年风华，军号嘹亮，在战位上坚守的那群可爱的人是如何庆祝建党百年的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-d5cf231e1fdee47e2e7f5abed68cf09f_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "171 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/roundtable/bainianfenghu